---
description: Post GitHub review based on LLM recommendation
mlld-version: ">=1.3.0"
---

# Post Review Comment

@import { * } from @input

## Set Default Values

@text recommendation = @LLM_RECOMMENDATION || "COMMENT"
@text reviewBody = @LLM_REVIEW_BODY || "Review failed to generate"
@text repo = @REPO_OWNER + "/" + @REPO_NAME

## Debug Output

@text debugMessage = [[Posting review for PR #{{PR_NUMBER}} with recommendation: {{recommendation}}]]
@add @debugMessage

## Post Review Based on Recommendation

@when @recommendation: [
  "APPROVE" => @run [(gh pr review @PR_NUMBER --repo @repo --approve --body "@reviewBody")]
  "REQUEST_CHANGES" => @run [(gh pr review @PR_NUMBER --repo @repo --request-changes --body "@reviewBody")]
  "COMMENT" => @run [(gh pr comment @PR_NUMBER --repo @repo --body "@reviewBody")]
]

## Summary

@add "âœ… Review posted successfully"